## Non-Retaliation

No individual shall be penalized in any way for having reported or threatened to report any violation of procedure, policy, or non-compliance with the *Code of Conduct, Equity & Inclusion*, or for cooperating with or participating in any grievance investigation. Furthermore, no individual shall be penalized for reporting incidents of discrimination, harassment, or sexual misconduct. Retaliation by any member of the community against such an individual is prohibited, and shall be considered a serious violation of Make School policy. Retaliation includes threats, intimidation, reprisals, and any adverse actions related to an individualâ€™s employment or 

Education.
